00:54:18.929 --> 00:54:20.100
Tae Kyung.

00:54:21.259 --> 00:54:23.830
Tío Dae Sang, mejor me voy.

00:54:23.929 --> 00:54:27.170
Estás borracha. Te llevaré a casa.

00:54:27.170 --> 00:54:30.469
